    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really? i feel like i'm just overreacting. the pain comes and goes sometimes so it doesnt feel like an 'emergency' every second. i've had cramps like this before and they were awful. is it actually appendicitis or could it just be something like a digestive thing? i'm just so tired and i don't want to sit in an ER for 8 hours if it's nothing.",
